ChatFusionAI
1. Project Title & Tagline
ChatFusionAI: SaaS LLM Orchestration & Content Personalization Engine
A production-ready database architecture for multi-tenant AI applications, featuring brand-voice injection, token-based usage limits, and performance-linked analytics.
2. Key AI Engineering Features
Dynamic Brand-Context Injection: The schema implements a sophisticated brand_profiles system. By storing tone, vocabulary, and guidelines as structured JSON, the platform enables "Prompt Engineering as a Service," ensuring LLM outputs are tailored to specific brand identities without manual prompt tweaking.
Token Economy & Cost Guardrails: Architected a robust app_settings layer that manages max_tokens_per_user and pricing_multiplier. This provides the infrastructure necessary to maintain profitability while interfacing with expensive third-party APIs (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.).
Generative Content Versioning: Unlike standard CMS platforms, ChatFusionAI tracks content_versions. This allows for a "Human-in-the-Loop" workflow where AI-generated drafts can be refined, rolled back, and compared for quality over time.
Success-Feedback Loop: Integrated an analytics_events system that tracks clicks and conversions against specific AI-generated content_ids. This allows the platform to theoretically perform Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback (RLHF) by identifying which AI "styles" perform best in the real world.
